ğŸ“Š Data Pipeline: Handles collection, cleaning, preprocessing, and feature engineering for climate, air quality, and epidemiology data.

âš–ï¸ Imbalance Handling: Applied SMOTE (Synthetic Minority Oversampling Technique) to balance minority disease outbreak classes.

ğŸ¤– Models Used:

Random Forest Classifier

